'''Biyoxidheen''' ({{lang-en|dam}}; {{lang-ar|سد}}) waa [[dhisme]] weyn oo ka samaysan [[dhagax]]aan, [[bir]]o iyo qalab kale oo badan kaasi oo loogu tallo galay in uu celiyo [[biyo|qulqulka biyaha]] socda. Biyoxidheenada waxaa loo dhisaa sababo badan oo ka mid tahay in laga sameeyo il biyo dadku isticmaalaan, laga sameeyo [[koronto]], laga waraabiyo [[beer|beeraha waaweyn]] iyo in la maamulo socodka iyo jihada biyaha.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bartleby.com/61/45/D0014500.html |title=Bartleby.com: Great Books Online – Quotes, Poems, Novels, Classics and hundreds more |date= |work=bartleby.com |accessdate=9 November 2015 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090408164742/http://www.bartleby.com:80/61/45/D0014500.html |archivedate=8 April 2009 |df=dmy }}http://www.bartleby.com/</ref>

Biyoxidheenadu waxay ka mid yihiin [[kaabayaal|kaabayaasha bulshada]] kuwaasi oo laga helo waxyaabaha aasaasiga ah ee isku xidha isla markaana u adeega magaalo, degmo, gobol, wadan iyo wixii la mid ah.<ref>. [http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/infrastructure Infrastructure | Define Infrastructure at Dictionary.com<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref> 
Sida caadiga ah, kaabayaashu waxay u adeegan ama isku xidhaan bulshada waxayna saldhig u yihiin koboca dhaqaale iyo guud ahaan isku socodka shaqada.<ref>{{cite book | last = O'Sullivan | first = Arthur | authorlink = Arthur O'Sullivan (economist) | first2=Steven M. | last2=Sheffrin | authorlink2 = Steven M. Sheffrin | title = Economics: Principles in Action | publisher = Pearson Prentice Hall | year = 2003 | location = Upper Saddle River, New Jersey 07458 | page = 474 | isbn = 0-13-063085-3}}</ref>

==Hordhac==
Biyoxidheenku wuxuu ka mid yahay waxyaabaha dabiiciga ah ee dadku uga faa'iideeystaan siyaabo badan. Waa marka horee, biyoxidheenadu waxay sameeyaan biyo keydsan oo dadka iyo xayawaanku isticmaali karaan. Sidoo kale, waxaa laga sameeyaa korontada biyaha oo ah hab raqiis ah oo lagu sameeyo koronto.<ref>Günther Garbrecht: "Wasserspeicher (Talsperren) in der Antike", ''Antike Welt'', 2nd special edition: ''Antiker Wasserbau'' (1986), pp.51–64 (52)</ref><ref>S.W. Helms: "Jawa Excavations 1975. Third Preliminary Report", Levant 1977</ref>

Kaabayaashu waa adeega aasaasiga ah ee bulsho kaasi oo fududeeya isku socodka, ganacisga, nolosha maalinle iyo dhamaanba baahida kala duwan ee bulsho.<ref>{{cite journal|last=Fulmer|first=Jeffrey|title=What in the world is infrastructure?|journal=PEI Infrastructure Investor|year=2009|issue=July/August|pages=30–32}}</ref>
